reviewText: Came quick and in mint condition! I will use this seller again. The dvd was very informative. The Standard Deviants series are great to use if you are just learning about a subject or if you want to learn more about a subject that your currently studying.

It definitely helps you understand the concepts of finance. I got hooked on these back in high school. I still think they're rather relevant. The presentation is a bit on the... strange side. It's the strangeness that makes it stick for you.
